/music/legendary-record-producer-steve-albini-has-died-aged-61-3754583">在此处</a>阅读。贾维斯·科克还回忆了在“进一步的并发症”期间与制片人合作对他产生的影响，您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jarvis-cocker-pays-tribute-to-unique-individual-steve-albini-3754664">在这里阅读他的完整致敬</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cribs-pay-tribute-its-hard-to-imagine-steve-albini-being-gone-3754782">The Cribs 的帖子致敬：“很难想象 Steve Albini 离开了”，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
